Rei - courtesy and etiquette, respect, propriety, ceremony, worship. Respect and gratitude to each other, to one's anchestors, to one's society, to nature and the universe nurtures conscious living and the world we live in. <br>
Source: http://www.bushidointernational.org/articles/hakama.htm <br>
